yaariyan ( english : friendships ) is a 2014 bollywood coming-of-age romance adventure film directed by divya khosla kumar , starring himansh kohli , rakul preet singh and nicole faria in the lead roles .   it marks the debut of the director as well as the lead star cast .   the film was produced by bhushan kumar and krishan kumar under the banner of t-series super cassettes industries .   yaariyan tells the story of 5 close friends who are in college , experiencing different relationships and learning new values .   the response to the promotional material on youtube led the distributor to release the film two weeks earlier than initially planned .   the film released on 10 january 2014 with 1200 screens release in india .